    "description": "《多元守卫者》是一款结合了Roguelike和自走棋元素的策略类游戏，玩家需要招募各种各样的英雄，并搭配独特的装备，抵御敌人的进攻，打倒最终Boss以获得胜利！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088040/extras/f831e2ab3666a0ac716d1c471344de59.poster.avif?t=1735078260\" width=600 height=352 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088040/extras/f831e2ab3666a0ac716d1c471344de59.webm?t=1735078260\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088040/extras/f831e2ab3666a0ac716d1c471344de59.mp4?t=1735078260\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >独特的羁绊</h2>和其他自走棋游戏一样，《多元守卫者》也有完整的阵营羁绊系统。在游玩过程中，你需要根据情况选择强力英雄，建立英雄小队。游戏里有非常多的英雄角色，从术士、神射手、剑舞者等，每个角色都有自己独特的属性和技能，相信你一定可以在里面找到喜欢的角色。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088040/extras/ded457a75487a4621f8d07fefad81d74.avif?t=1735078260\" width=615 height=290 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >多样的装备</h2>在这款游戏中，装备系统是一个极为丰富和多样化的核心特色。玩家游戏中收集各种装备，包括剑、刀、杖等等，这些装备拥有不同的品质和随机属性。同时装备还能够附魔以添加套装效果。通过给英雄配搭合适的装备可以大幅度提高战斗力。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088040/extras/7bfe15cd8e69555d2beb01007f2f5acf.avif?t=1735078260\" width=614 height=600 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >丰富的宝物</h2>宝物能够配合玩家的成长路线。它们可以提高玩家的战斗力、经济收益等等。玩家需要根据英雄阵型发展方向来进行宝物选择，快速提阵型强度，为Boss决斗的时候做铺垫。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088040/extras/8bf2d3a293125ae881bc70984508e866.avif?t=1735078260\" width=614 height=360 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >强大的Boss</h2>在游戏中，玩家每经过一定的关卡便会遇到强大的Boss，每个Boss都拥有不同的技能，针对不同的Boss打造独有的战斗策略才是制胜的关键。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088040/extras/bda5ec33296f269a45c0132b40d63e6f.poster.avif?t=1735078260\" width=600 height=352 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088040/extras/bda5ec33296f269a45c0132b40d63e6f.webm?t=1735078260\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088040/extras/bda5ec33296f269a45c0132b40d63e6f.mp4?t=1735078260\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
